def my_func(n):
    if n == 0 or n == 1000000:
        return n
    if n < 10:
        return n * n
    if n < 100:
        return n * (100 - n)
    if n < 1000:
        return n * (1000 - n)
    if n < 10000:
        return n * (10000 - n)
    if n < 100000:
        return n * (100000 - n)
    if n < 1000000:
        return n * (1000000 - n)
